{% extends "core/emails/base.html.j2" %}
{% block title %}Upload your first SBOM - sbomify{% endblock %}
{% block content %}
    <h1>Time to upload your first SBOM, {{ user.first_name|default:user.username }}!</h1>
    <p>
        Nice work creating your first component! The next step is uploading an SBOM.
        Once uploaded, you can enable plugins for vulnerability scanning and compliance checks.
    </p>
    <p>You have two options:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
            <strong>GitHub Action (recommended):</strong> Use our
            <a href="https://github.com/sbomify/sbomify-action" target="_blank">GitHub Action</a>
            to generate and upload SBOMs automatically with every push
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Manual upload:</strong> Already have an SBOM? Upload it directly. We support
            both SPDX and CycloneDX formats
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
        <a href="{{ app_base_url }}/components/" class="button">Upload Your First SBOM</a>
    </p>
    <p>Got questions? Just reply to this email.</p>
{% endblock %}
